The '''Undying Flame''' was the cult of [[Yun-Txiin]] and [[Yun-Q'aah]], the [[Lover Gods]] of the [[Yuuzhan Vong]]. Their [[Priest caste|priests]], called the [[Apostle]]s of the Undying Flame, usually mutilated their bodies so that one side appeared [[Gender/Legends|male]], representing Yun-Txiin, and another side female, representing Yun-Q'aah. The Undying Flame counseled those who had found love, but if this love was between those of different [[Yuuzhan Vong castes|castes]], the Apostles would immediately sacrifice the unlucky lovers to Yun-Txiin and Yun-Q'aah.

